Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.67,0:22:40.96,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}倘若不变得强大
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.48,0:22:43.87,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}我将失去生存的意义
